882    <S {Ies}.> His words were farewell mistris, nothing else.
883    <S {Shy}.> The patch is kinde enough, but a huge feeder:
884    Snaile- slow in profit, but he sleepes by day
885    More then the wilde- cat: drones hiue not with me,
886    Therefore I part with him, and part with him
887    To one that I would haue him helpe to waste
888    His borrowed purse. Well {Iessica} goe in,
889    Perhaps I will returne immediately;
890   *Doe as I bid you, shut dores after you, fast binde, fast
