1577   My purpose was not to haue seene you heere,
1578   But meeting with {Salerio} by the way,
1579   He did intreate mee past all saying nay
1580   To come with him along.
1581   <S {Sal}.> I did my Lord,
1582   And I haue reason for it, Signior {Anthonio}
1583   Commends him to you.
